            <div class="reveal">
                <h2>Consent Mode v2</h2>
                <p>
                    Categories used by this site: <code>analytics_storage</code>,
                    <code>ad_storage</code>, <code>ad_user_data</code>,
                    <code>ad_personalization</code>, <code>functionality_storage</code>,
                    <code>personalization_storage</code>, <code>security_storage</code>.
                    Default state is <strong>granted</strong> (opt-out model). The consent
                    banner flips every category except <code>security_storage</code> to
                    <strong>denied</strong> if you click "Reject".
                </p>
