            <div class="reveal">
                <h2>How to turn tracking off</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click <strong>Reject</strong> on the consent banner if it appears. If it's already dismissed, clear <code>bh_cookie_consent</code> from your browser cookies and reload — the banner will re-appear.</li>
                    <li>Or use your browser's "Do Not Track" / cookie-blocking settings.</li>
                    <li>Or install a content-blocker like uBlock Origin or Privacy Badger — this site does not try to detect or circumvent them.</li>
                </ol>
